&lt;p&gt;Want to self-publish a book?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Want to have all the recipes for&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ebook-writing with sensible defaults for

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PDF&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;mobi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EPUB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HTML&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;text&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;all the packages/tools/everything and the kitchensink installed and prepared for your preasure? (free)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a static website, hosted for free on Github with your own top-level domain? (free)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment with Stripe (2.5% + $0.30)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Newsletter Management with Sandy ($0.10 per 1,000)&lt;/li&gt;
