&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s create &lt;code&gt;package&lt;/code&gt;, that will have all the stuff you&amp;rsquo;ll need to start writing your next best-selling Ebook right after installing!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Wait no longer, go here!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;https://github.com/mindreframer/vagrant-kitabu
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

